<dl id="n42011d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42011d">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42011d"> 11(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> W. he had confessed</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">It was not very long after my ordination when a priest came to me to confess the most deplorable things. He honestly told me that there was not a single one of the girls or married women whom he had confessed who had not been a secret cause of the most shameful sins, in thought, desires, or actions; <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 36</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
